robert walter weir june 18 , 1803 - may 1 , 1889 american artist , best know educator , historical painter . 
consider artist hudson river school , elect national academy design 1829 , instructor united states military academy . 
among better-known work : embarkation pilgrims rotunda united states capitol washington , d.c. ; landing hendrik hudson ; evening crucifixion ; columbus council salamanca ; lord mount olives ; virgil dante cross styx . 
